## Environment Variables — Both Platforms

```bash
# Public (browser-safe — must have NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix):
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[ref].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...   # new projects
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...                       # legacy projects
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...

# Server-only (NEVER use NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix):
SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY=sb_secret_...           # new projects
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...            # legacy projects
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
REVALIDATION_SECRET=[random-32-char-string]

# Netlify: set per deploy context (production / preview / branch)
# Vercel:  set per environment (production / preview / development)
```

