## Common Deployment Errors

| Error | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `cookies()` called in static context | Auth code on statically-rendered page | Add `export const dynamic = 'force-dynamic'` |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` undefined at runtime | Env var set server-only in platform | Move to correct client-accessible env var |
| Images 404 from Supabase | Missing `remotePatterns` in `next.config.ts` | Add Supabase hostname pattern |
| Function timeout on Netlify free | Default 10 s limit | Increase to 26 s in Netlify dashboard or use Edge Function |
| API route 413 on large upload | Serverless body limit | Stream direct to Supabase Storage from client using TUS |
| `params` / `searchParams` TypeError | Not awaiting in Next.js 15.2+ | `const { id } = await params` — see `rocket-nextjs-patterns.mdc` |

