## Deployment Checklist (both platforms)

```
Before first deploy:
  ✅ All env vars set in platform dashboard (not just .env.local)
  ✅ NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL = production project URL (not localhost)
  ✅ Auth redirect URLs include your production domain
  ✅ next.config.ts: remotePatterns includes Supabase storage hostname
  ✅ No console.log in production TypeScript files
  ✅ All Server Actions validate auth as first step

After first deploy:
  ✅ Sign-up → email confirmation → sign-in flow works end-to-end
  ✅ /api/health returns 200
  ✅ Images load from Supabase Storage
  ✅ Stripe webhooks reachable (test with stripe listen --forward-to)
  ✅ Run Lighthouse on production URL → target 90+ Performance
```
